name: PSYCHEDELIC MIRROR
description:
Resolution: 8K (7680 x 4320)
feat @GummyLSD 

Watching your true self
in the mirror of your mortal shell,
your sweet heart, like a candy, melts,
overtaken by an indigo spell.

Truth can shock you my dear friend,
it's just more than we can stand,
just remember that we are safe here,
there's nothing but yourself fear.

Your dark side is on your side,
but is not something to hide,
that was pushing your heart to dare
to become a colored gummy bear.
